text: Antioch is an unincorporated community in Posey Township, Switzerland County, in the U.S. state of Indiana. ==History== A post office was established at Antioch in 1894, and remained in operation until it was discontinued in 1902. ==Geography== Antioch is located at . ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Switzerland County, Indiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Indiana
